title: Episode 255: Broken Pussy (Feat. Issa Rae)
itunes:title: Episode 255: Broken Pussy (Feat. Issa Rae)
description:
Issa Rae breaks down the complex relationship between Issa and Molly on HBO’s Insecure, and the awkward dynamic with Condola. Issa opens up about a vacation gone wrong (in her real life), as well as the one place on her body she does not want to be touched. Make sure to check out her 2 latest movies, The Photograph and The Love Birds, and of course, HBO’s Insecure!
